item.title: Usage
item.description: Usage credate [OPTION] [FILEs...] OPTIONS -b, --byte Prints the number of bytes in each input file. -c, --character Prints the number of characters in each input file. -l, --line Prints the number of lines in each input file. -w, --word Prints the number of words in each input file. -d, --date Prints the creation date of file. -h, --help Prints this message.
